# Asserts ffiCompile input-hash caching:
#  1. initial compile → artifact produced
#  2. snapshot its mtime
#  3. re-run with no changes → cache hit, mtime unchanged
#  4. swap in a new C source body → cache miss, artifact rebuilt
> ffiCompile
> snapshotCompileMtime
> assertCompileUnchanged
$ delete src/main/c/lib.c
$ copy-file template/lib_v2.c src/main/c/lib.c
> ffiCompile
> assertCompileChanged
